{"tid":1445152,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"係咪唔記得左一個都不能少","createTime":"2019-08-11T13:59:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T15:47:09.000Z","uid":49383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"a9ee34b95ddb41edf098b2bcf424d3135f17c31a","tid":1445152,"uid":49383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T13:59:27.000Z","msg":"岩岩翻到屋企睇now新聞 <br />\n尖沙咀有位有足俾2隻狗捉左 <br />\n身邊有幾百個人係側邊逃走<br />\n我無睇錯 好多都係戴晒頭盔既手足<br />\n我真係忍唔住講一句 DLLM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n得兩隻狗cap住位手足 你地幾百人<br />\n唔好話逃走 溶左果兩隻狗都仲得<br />\n但你地不停跑 俾人捉住位手足係幾咁絕望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n望住幾百人係身邊跑 都無人幫自己 <br />\n走還走 散還散<br />\n請大家記住 一個都不能少 就算be water<br />\n都最起碼救翻身邊位手足 救一個得一個<br />\n我真係好嬲 嬲到喊 Sorry <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請大家記住 我地人數佔絕對優勢<br />\n要救人 絕對唔難 <br />\n<br />\n <strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">一個都不能少呀</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"1487f73dee0714dd3c33930ce5d3d76ba0988dc4","tid":1445152,"uid":49383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:23:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6cf3b89085d91476f1960b8ab3d920fd259560cb","tid":1445152,"uid":49383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:35:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b1b373df0193b39890cfe6cc98da74ab785a7163","tid":1445152,"uid":49383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:58:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c1c42dea51ae92242f67ce9728d1566006940f21","tid":1445152,"uid":49383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T15:47:09.000Z","msg":"推"}]}